data.description:
Welcome to 4076 Cactus Dr in the growing city of Argyle. Located in the sought after Argyle
School district. When purchasing a mobile home, you usually find yourself too close to the
neighbors and without a fence to divide your property... not in this case! This 2020 modern
Jessup Model Sigle-Wide Mobile home sits on nearly a quarter of an acre of land (.194), fenced on
all sides, with a few trees that offer shade and also a couple of Fruit trees!
This property offers the best of both worlds: privacy and quietness but also only a 9 Minute
drive to I35W
